transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hi Prasad sir, good morning. Vasundhara here from IndiaMART. How are you sir?
Customer: Bolo bolo. [unintelligible]
Executive: Ha bolo madam.
Customer: Sir, woh aapka na ek call aaya tha jiski wajah se aapka ek ticket open hua hai. Toh aapko just call kiya tha koi issue aa raha hai service mein, koi feedback ke liye kya ek tatari hai sir?
Customer: Kuch nahi mai renewal nahi karta hu abhi. Abhi paisa nahi hai mere paas.
Executive: Sir, lekin aapka itna purana company online presence chal raha hai yaha pe. Thik hai, baki ka aise hi bataiye mujhe ticket aaya tha koi, aise hi mujhe bataiye service mein koi issue toh nahi hai na?
Customer: Yeh do saal ka business nahi hai madam. [inaudible] karna hai renewal.
Executive: Sir yeh batao pehle mujhe service mein koi issue toh nahi hai aapko?
Customer: Business nahi hai madam.
Executive: Nahi nahi, mai puch rahi hu ki service mein jo aapne ticket open kiya tha not satisfy mark kiya tha call ke upar. Toh kya service mein kuch problem aa rahi hai iski wajah se aapne not satisfy mark kiya tha?
Customer: Abhi baad mein abhi driving hai baad mein baat karta hu aap se.
Executive: Accha yeh bataiye sir, mai aapka jo feedback aaya tha woh close kar du? Aur koi issue na ho service ke regarding mein toh aapko?
Customer: [unintelligible]
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer does not want to renew subscription.

- Customer marked 'not satisfied' on a call.



Resolution:

- Executive inquired about the reason for dissatisfaction.

- Executive offered to close the feedback ticket.



Next Steps: 

- Issue not resolved. Customer will call later.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- renewal, feedback, dissatisfaction, service
